Dialogue: 9,0:00:02.02,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha aquela coisa\Nvazando do G491!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas estão usando o sinal do Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda é um Gauna!{shortened sentence}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenham o ataque!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O G490 está corrompendo o quadro 139.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As estacas placentárias\Nperfuraram o quadro.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro aqui,\Nrelatando um quadro destruído.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,É... você... Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:31.01,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não avance!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue me ouvir?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.02,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles não entendem o que você está dizendo!
