Dialogue: 9,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso está em conformidade com a lei de emigração
Dialogue: 9,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,que afirma que um pedido de emigração de 50.000 ou mais deve ser concedido.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Estima-se que até 100.000 possam eventualmente emigrar.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:36.38,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles realmente ficarão bem com o aglomerado de colmeias por perto?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:39.80,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As pessoas que embarcam nos navios de emigração acham que os Gauna não atacarão se você não tiver um Kabizashi.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é ridículo.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:46.81,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que estamos desperdiçando recursos com esses malucos?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não acha que isso aumenta as chances de sobrevivência da humanidade?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Não é o declínio populacional\Num problema muito maior para nós?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente seremos promovidos,\Ncom a falta de pessoal.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo o que todo mundo fala\Né a emigração.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo está realmente dividido\Nsobre o assunto.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me pergunto o que vai\Nacontecer agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, você está me ouvindo, Nagate?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, claro.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Então fale comigo.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Um...]
Dialogue: 9,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Honestamente...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 9,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Viu?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:33.27,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoje eles têm ensopado de gravidade no refeitório dos pilotos.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda não.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Não ligo para isso.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:41.44,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, isso não te diz respeito,\Npor ser o novato que você é.{so rekt lel}
Dialogue: 9,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 9,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Quer ir comer lá?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpem vocês dois.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:52.79,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles querem que eu vá para o EBD.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O EBD?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,De novo?{s/he sounds like a jealous bitch}
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar então.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Hoshijiro...]
Dialogue: 9,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Afasta-te!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, espere.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Naquela época...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece que acalmou.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tente conversar com ele.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, tá bom.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Hum...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Hoshi... jiro...]
Dialogue: 9,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta... [T0ni... ka... ze...[T1]]
Dialogue: 9,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta... ni... [T0ka... ze...[T1]]
Dialogue: 9,0:14:14.20,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta... ni... ka... [T0ze...[T1]]
Dialogue: 9,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta... ni... ka... ze...[T0[T1]]
Dialogue: 9,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tá... n-i-k-a... zé...{** kun.}
Dialogue: 9,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Respondeu?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx100}...{\r} Hoshijiro, eu—
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnZekton Rg\b1\fax0.26\frx4\fry356\fs46\blur5\be5\alpha&H50&\c&H80F3F4&\frz7.186\pos(622,232)} Ordem de Saída
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnZekton Rg\b1\fax0.26\frx4\fry356\fs46\blur0.5\c&H80F3F4&\frz7.186\pos(622,232)} Ordem de Saída
Dialogue: 9,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho que sair em missão.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um único Gauna entrou no nosso alcance de sensores.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Está cruzando a linha de defesa nível um.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}Apenas um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É o Benisuzume?{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Repassando.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,É um Gauna tipo H1.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Os pilotos devem embarcar mais rápido.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuide disso, o mais longe possível.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que Tsugumori tem um Kabizashi?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Porque você é o lançador.{i hope people wont see this as a fate reference, because it isnt. ive been trying to treat the gardes squads as cavalry units where possible, and a lancer is a mounted lance-wielding soldier, so i think this is the best possible translation. id accept alternative translations for soldiers wielding spears or lances if they dont sound dumb}{seems fine to me}
Dialogue: 9,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seii[T0.]
Dialogue: 9,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoje, eu estarei no seu esquadrão.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prazer em conhecê-lo, Líder de Esquadrão Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um líder de esquadrão?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nada!
